headline: Top Picks 2026- Prologis Inc. PLD
summary: My growth-oriented pick entering 2026 is Prologis Inc. (PLD), the global leader in logistics real estate. With roughly 1.3 billion square feet of warehouses in high-barrier, high-growth markets worldwide, Prologis sits at the center of the global movement of goods and functions as essential infrastructure, highlights Nikolaos Sismanis, analyst at Sure Retirement.
